message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously crafted to provide exceptional value and quality. Given its unique features and benefits, I believe it's worth more than $100. Considering the high standards and effort put into this product, I kindly propose a price of $150 for you to experience its full potential. I trust this investment will prove worthwhile for you. If you're interested, please let me know, and we can proceed with the transaction.
